{
  "id": "adv_main_02_06_03",
  "title": "東京編2章3話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n昨日姫野さんに会ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\ndid you really go see Himeno-san yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3333333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "どうして先に教えてくれなかったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why didn’t you tell us first?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.133333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、こんな朝早くからどうした！？\nそれにどうして姫野さんのこと知って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Girls‚ why are you all up so early?!\nAnd how did you know about Himeno-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "昨夜、姫野さんから私達にメッセージが届いたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Himeno-san sent us a message last night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達にもです\nあの人、プレタポルテに移ったんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Us‚ too.\nShe transferred over to Pret-A-Porter‚ didn’t she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女達にも直接揺さぶりをかけたのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So‚ she’s approaching them directly…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "父は……朝倉社長は……\n本当に横領をしていたんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My father… President Asakura…\nI guess he really did embezzle‚ then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの人がそう言ったからといって真実とは限らないよ\nなんだか、俺はあの人を信用出来ないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just because she said so‚ that doesn’t mean it’s true.\nI don’t know why‚ but I don’t trust her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "一応言っておくけど、LizNoirは\nプレタポルテには行かないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me just make this clear. LizNoir\nwill not be transferring to Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "これは私だけじゃなく、メンバー全員の意見よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not just speaking for myself; we all feel the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あの人、事務所の力で星見プロを潰すって\n脅したらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like she threatened to use her agency’s power\nto crush Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、ウ、ウチを潰すって……それ、本当ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? C-crush us? Is that true?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私も優に聞きました……\nすみません、私達のせいで、みなさんにご迷惑を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu told me the news‚ too.\nI’m sorry. All of this is our fault…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "違う。瑠依さんは何も悪くないです\nここにいる誰も悪くなんかない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. You did nothing wrong‚ Rui.\nNobody at this agency did anything wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それに私達のせいなんて言い方やめて下さい\nトリエルはもう星見プロ所属の仲間なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And please‚ stop using terms like “our fault.”\nTRINITYAiLE is part of Hoshimi Productions now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 85.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、琴乃ちゃんの言う通りだよ\n瑠依ちゃん、まだ他人行儀なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Kotono-chan is absolutely right.\nRui‚ why do you always distance yourself from us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、さくら……\nありがとうございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… Sakura…\nI am grateful to you both.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "もう瑠依ちゃん、まだ固いよ？\nありがとうでいいんだってば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ loosen up‚ will you?\nJust say‚ “thanks.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、ありがとうござい――あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right. Thank y… oops!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、瑠依はそういう所\n不器用ね。可愛いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Rui is real awkward\nwhen it comes to these sorts of things. It’s kinda cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ほっといて下さい。莉央さんだってリズノワの\n公式SNSに可愛い画像アップしてるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave me alone. What about you‚ Rio-san?\nYou’re always posting cute photos of yourself on the official LizNoir SNS.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私が？　私はそんな覚えは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Me? I have no memory of that—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は、パンケーキを美味しそうに\n食べてる画像が上がっていましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You uploaded a photo of yourself\neating yummy-looking pancakes yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん、一昨日も別のパンケーキを食べてましたよね！\n今度、私も連れてって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ and the day before‚ you were eating another type of pancake!\nTake me with you next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 137.03333333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 137.53333333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7299.999999999983,
          "startTime": 137.73333333333332
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7500,
          "startTime": 137.93333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、ちょっと待って\n今確認するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a minute!\nLet me check the site.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……こころの仕業ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s Kokoro’s dirty work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、こころちゃんが\n莉央さんに無許可でアップしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Kokoro did that?\nShe uploaded those pics without Rio-san's permission?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "『本日の可愛い莉央ちゃん』ってコーナー\n前から人気なんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To a section called “Cute Rio Pic of the Day.”\nIt’s been popular for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子、帰ったら20キロ走らせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we get back‚ I’m making her run 20 kilometers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
