      "text": "お姉ちゃんとはいろいろ話したんですよね？\n仕事のことでお互いに悩みを打ち明けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You talked a lot of your problems over with my sister‚ didn’t you?\nYou shared your work problems with each other.",
